    <item>
      <title>法国集装箱运输巨头暂停红海航线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/french-container-shipping-giant-cma-cgm-halts-red-sea-transits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于安全风险，法国集装箱运输巨头达飞轮船暂停了其船只通过红海的航线，这意味着该行业最后的主要公司之一现在认为由于胡塞武装分子一直在发动袭击，该地区太不安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/french-container-shipping-giant-cma-cgm-halts-red-sea-transits</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 16:43:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于就业数据扰乱降息押注，美元触及枢轴前水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/dollar-hits-near-pre-pivot-level-as-job-data-roils-rate-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在井喷式就业报告发布后，美元出现两周来最大涨幅，将美元推回到美联储12月转向以及押注即将降息之前的错误水平之前的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/dollar-hits-near-pre-pivot-level-as-job-data-roils-rate-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 16:37:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ION Markets 取消 17 亿美元杠杆贷款重新定价交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/ion-markets-pulls-1-7-billion-leveraged-loan-sale-for-repricing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Andrea Pignataro 金融科技帝国旗下的 ION Markets 放弃了降低 17 亿美元贷款利率的努力，因为对该集团整体债务的担忧导致其债务市值下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/ion-markets-pulls-1-7-billion-leveraged-loan-sale-for-repricing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 14:57:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>热门就业数据令降息希望破灭，国债收益率飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/treasury-yields-jump-on-payrolls-traders-pare-rate-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[强于预期的 1 月份就业数据强化了美联储将降息至少推迟到第二季度的理由，美国国债收益率飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/treasury-yields-jump-on-payrolls-traders-pare-rate-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 13:44:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于降息希望高涨，英国债券跌破今年最差开局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/gilts-set-for-full-rally-after-paring-record-bad-start-to-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府债券出现一个多月以来的首次周度上涨，这让策略师和投资者更加大胆，他们表示涨势才刚刚开始。]]></description>
